Allegheny International Inc said chairman chief operating officer remain position following merger company affiliate First Boston Corp. `` It expected Oliver S. Travers continue chairman , president Chief executive officer , Thomas J. Albani continue chief operating officer , '' said Allegheny spokesman .
Allegheny today said agreed buyout First Boston 24.60 dlrs per share .
The transaction valued 500 mln dlrs .
Its stock rose 8-5/8 24 active trading .
